d with extreme humility and humbleness while fright and terror has reached its final extent and helplessness has become immense, the anticipators are incapable of further perseverance and You O Allah are in ambush for the schemers, You have not let them loose in spite of Your respite for them, only he who relies upon You relaxes in peace, who desires You is benefitting, who intends Your door, O Allah, is secured.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ مَنَاهِلُ كَرَامَاتِكَ بِجَزِیْلِ عَطِیَّاتِكَ مُتْرَعَۃٌ، وَاَبْوَابُ مُنَاجَاتِكَ لِمَنْ اَمَّكَ مُشْرَعَۃٌ۔ وَعَطُوْفُ لَحَظٰاتِكَ لِمَنْ ضَرَعَ اِلَیْكَ غَیْرُ مُنْقَطِعَۃٍ، وَقَدْ اُلْجِمَ الْحِذَارُ، وَاشْتَدَّ الْاِضْطِرَارُ، وَعَجَزَ عَنِ الْاِصْطِبَارِ اَهْلُ الْاِنْتِظَارِ وَاَنْتَ اللّٰھُمَّ بِالْمَرْصَدِ مِنَ الْمُكَّارِ، وَغَیْرُ مُهْمَلٍ مَّعَ الْاِمْهَالِ، وَاللّٰائِذُ بِكَ آمِنْ، وَالرَّاغِبُ اِلَیْكَ غَانِمٌ، وَالْقَاصِدُ اللّٰھُمَّ لِبَابِكَ سَالِمٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBl